Package: fontlens
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: archerprojects <archer.projects@proton.me>
Description: Font browser and comparison tool
 Lightweight font browser. Browse and scan any directory, compare fonts
 side by side, install to ~/.fonts with one click. No database, no indexing,
 no activation.
Depends: fontconfig, xdg-utils, libglib2.0-bin
